lyrics.text:
Some can't be tamed
All animals play games
I caught the plague in my
Butterfly net

All of the noise
Escaping from my voice
Conversating in my brain

We'll work it out
We'll burn it to the ground

Can you hear it?
Can you hear it?
Can you hear it so close?
Can you hear it?
Can you hear it?
Can you hear it so close?
